        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: 'But... if that\\'s the case, what could the School... possibly be up to?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'It clearly wields great power and resources, but it hasn\\'t unveiled its purpose to the world.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'During Operation Acadia, around the outbreak of the Punishing Virus, the School had never showed up...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Perhaps because they had already deemed the surface world as \"failures.\"', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'If the School regarded itself as an Ark, then it must be operating on the premise that the rest of the world will be destroyed by some kind of \"flood.\"', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'In other words, maybe the School went into hiding underground because they believed that the surface couldn\\'t endure the coming disaster.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...They sure sound full of themselves.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'That may be true, but... judging from the Gray Ravens\\' intel, no humans have been found in the facility.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'How is that possible? What about those that were identified as missing by the operation...?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: '...There were at least hundreds of thousands of people. But so far, none of the footage sent by the Gray Ravens indicated any signs of life.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: 'Are they hiding?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'They aren\\'t stupid. They should know that there would be no use hiding if someone has infiltrated their facility.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Could it be that something happened in the facility...?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'But we still haven\\'t reestablished contact with Gray Raven. It means that they still haven\\'t returned from the depths of the underground facility to an area where they can communicate.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '...Let\\'s just wait and see. Isn\\'t that what you told me?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Celica', 3: '\"Even if 【kuroname】 sees the darkness buried within this world, the commandant still manages to find one\\'s own direction in life.\"', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
